channel.title: Omg wtf?
channel.description:
When I run my server and my DUC(no-ip) and my uTorrent(I portforward with uTorrent) I try to log into my server using any ip. my no-ip, 0.0.0.0, 127.0.0.1 - none of those work. I get this message when i have uTorrent running while trying to log into my server. When i close uTorrent i can play. I think I NEED uTorrent open to host my server?
